data.description: This adorable home has so much to offer! It is nestled away on a quiet street located in a cul de sac.  4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom split floorplan. Large living room with a wood burning fireplace. Spacious master bedroom with ensuite, dual vanities, separate tub/shower, and huge walk in closet. It has a great size backyard that is fully fenced in. Rear yard access with plenty of concrete for parking vehicles or even boats. Roof and solar panels were newly installed in 2020. Solar panels will REMAIN with the purchase of the home. This one wont last long, scheudle your appointment today!!
